        <div n="Z198090A" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="triplet"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>wo or three dears and two or three sweets</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-2"> Two or three Balls and two or three treats;</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-3"> Two or three serenades giv'n as a lure;</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-4"> Two or three Oaths how much they endure;</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-5"> Two or three messages sent in one day:</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-6"> Two or three times led out from a play,</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-7"> Two or three soft speeches made by the way:</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-8"> Two or three Tickets for two or three times</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-9"> Two or three love letters writ all in rhymes,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-10"> Two or three months keeping strict to these rules</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-Z198090A-line-11"> Can never fail making a couple of fools.Z198090A   </l></lg></div>
